FBIS3-15110 "drsov042_b_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-042 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Stepashin Appointed Counterintelligence Chief LD0303082394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0750 GMT 3 Mar 94 LD0303082394 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS] [Text] Moscow March 3 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin signed a decree on Thursday appointing Sergey Stepashin head of the federal counter-intelligence service of the Russian Federation, the presidential press-service reported today.
